description.text: Welcome to The PopMod Flat at Hyde Midtown! Featured in Luxe Interiors & Design magazine, this rare three-bedroom, four-bath, completely updated, designer corner unit is punchy, modern, luxurious, and fun! Experience spacious picture-perfect living with designer wallpaper, luxe high-end finishes and fixtures, custom window treatments, and California Closets. Impress your guests with breath-taking Biscayne Bay and Downtown Miami balcony viewsand wait until they see the adorable Instagram-ready powder room! Sleep easy in the main suite retreat with dual vanity ensuite bath, separate from the two spacious ensuite guest rooms. All surrounded by trendy Midtown Miami shops, restaurants, and gyms, with one assigned parking, 24-hour security, and flexible 30-day minimum rental allowances.
